{
  "stem": "58.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You didn't hear a sound anymore. 3,100 people, it took about two hours to get rid of them in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "See, now I'm getting a little bit-- it gets to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they put us back in the cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the morning we cam in from Treblinka back to Lublin-- city of Lublin, it's very close to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, they got--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he's ready, I'm ready, I told you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came into Lublin, we were told that they already have-- the Germans also make mistake.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If not, God forbid, they would have won the war-- if they wouldn't make mistakes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were told that the ghetto has already 500 Greek Jews cleaning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, they'll send us into Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not that the-- We came into Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not a camp, it was a-- a torture chamber, the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They also had a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were fields, there were 1, 2, 3, 4, as I remember, I don't know if there was a 5, also.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They call it a field.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Second field, they called Kanada, because the people worked to sort the clothes that came in from all the-- from all the gas chambers, from the people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they sorted it, so they found money, all kind of jewelry, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People took with, they were told they were going to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They found francs, that people came from-- from France, transports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They, I was sent to the third field.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I came in, and we're sent into horse-- horse barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nothing, no beds, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Just straw sacks on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And nighttime-- in the morning, you put-- stuck them up against the wall, and at nighttime, you pull them down.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was not yours, whatever you picked.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
